                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The giant pangolin releases a disorienting and repulsive musk within a 5-foot emanation. Each creature in the area must attempt a <span data-pf2-check=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-dc=\"20\" data-pf2-traits=\"olfactory\" data-pf2-label=\"Emit Musk DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Fortitude</span> save.</p>\n<p>The pangolin can't Emit Musk again for [[/br 1d4 #rounds]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature becomes temporarily immune to pangolin musk for 1 minute.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened 1} and is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Flat-Footed]{Flat-Footed} until no longer sickened.</p>"
                },
